Package com.landawn.abacus.util

Class Builder<T>

java.lang.Object
com.landawn.abacus.util.Builder<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of the value this Builder can hold.
Direct Known Subclasses:
Builder.BooleanListBuilder, Builder.ByteListBuilder, Builder.CharListBuilder, Builder.CollectionBuilder, Builder.DataSetBuilder, Builder.DoubleListBuilder, Builder.FloatListBuilder, Builder.IntListBuilder, Builder.LongListBuilder, Builder.MapBuilder, Builder.MultimapBuilder, Builder.MultisetBuilder, Builder.ShortListBuilder, Builder.X
public class Builder<T> extends Object
This class represents a Builder that can hold a value of type T. It provides methods to perform operations on the value it holds, such as mapping, filtering, and applying functions. The class also includes nested classes for building specific types of objects, such as lists, maps, and data sets.
See Also:
  • ImmutableList.builder()
  • ImmutableSet.builder()
